<figureCitation box="[159,245,551,575]" captionStart="FIGURES 22 – 30" captionStartId="18.[151,264,1546,1569]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,193,1525]" captionTargetId="figure@18.[151,1436,193,1525]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURES 22 – 30. Head and pronotum of Frankliniella spp. (22) F. annulipes; (23) F. australis; (24) F. bertelsi; (25) F. brevicaulis; (26) F. brunnea; (27) F. c u r t a; (28) F. distinguenda; (29) F. frumenti; (30) F. fulvipennis." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/246164/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
